 • airspaces which are 150 meters above ground or water surface level 16

• the unmanned aircrafts and surroundings are kept within the visual line of sight of the operator;

 • a certain operating distance (30 meters) 17  is maintained between unmanned aircrafts and persons or properties on the ground or water surface;

 • no flying over festival or event sites where many people are gathered;

 • no transport of explosives, flammables, or other hazardous materials;

 • no dropping of any object except for the goods specified in the relevant ordinance.
